  "text": "The subjects with schizotypal personality disorder met criteria for a number of comorbid personality and axis I disorders, including paranoid (N=6) and borderline (N=5) personality disorders, depression (N=2), dysthymia (N=1), panic disorder (N=1), alcohol abuse (N=1), and polysubstance abuse (N=1); all substance abuse occurred more than 2 years before testing. More information concerning the subjects' characteristics is available elsewhere [CITATION_1] .",
